  _missions:
  - Act: 1
    QuestId: arrive
    Title: Homecoming
    Summary: Recognize Wren at the village well.
  - Act: 1
    QuestId: speakBram
    Title: The Crooked Pintle
    Summary: Give Wren the mill key and what news he can bear to tell.
  - Act: 1
    QuestId: firstSale
    Title: Marra's Kitchen
    Summary: Buy Wren's first basket and bring Marra into the room.
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: meetHollin
    Title: A Stranger at the Inn
    Summary: Host the traveler who asks for Wren by name.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: festivalHosted
    Title: The First Festival in Three Years
    Summary: Restore the Pintle's lanterns and public place in village life.
  _quotes:
  - Text: Lord help me. You've got your father's height.
    Context: Recognizing Wren after three winters.
  - Text: Wheel hasn't turned since the Wend went and changed its mind about where
      it was going.
    Context: Explaining what happened to the mill.
  - Text: I remember where the lantern hooks go. Mostly.
    Context: Preparing for Hollowfen's festival.
